Returns:
    A message indicating the success or failure of the object creation and a screenshot of the object.

Examples:
    If you want to create a cylinder with a height of 30 and a radius of 10, you can use the following data.
    ```json
    {
        "doc_name": "MyCylinder",
        "obj_name": "Cylinder",
